    en: "Chinese culture reveres \u2018harmony\u2019 \u2014 a concept with deep roots. \u2018Harmony\u2019 is seen as the origin of all things, the key to moral cultivation, the standard for social interaction, and the principle for nations coexisting. Explore the meaning and role of \u2018harmony.\u2019"
